<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>とにかく……やったな、リオン！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyway... we did it, Leon!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>すまない、事情があるんだ。
……せめて代金は置いていく</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry, I have my own circumstances.
...I'll at least leave payment.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それが３時間並ばなきゃ買えない
ピーチパイか。
おいしそうだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's the peach pie you have to wait about
3 hours to buy? It looks so yummy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン……このピーチパイを
狙うというのなら
たとえお前でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn... If you're after this peach pie,
even if it's you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わっ、じょ、冗談だって！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa, I-I'm just joking!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>でもよかったな。
これでリオンの大切な人も
解放されるんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I'm happy for you. That person that's really
important to you will be released now, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいや、まだだ。
次の要求が届いている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, not yet.
The next demand just arrived.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>BG01a.ppt</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>0</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
